OL,3,CHeadteacher stole from two schools
OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FA disgraced headteacher has been
OL,8,Fjailed for stealing more than #15,000
OL,9,Ffrom two primary schools in Liverpool.
OL,11,FNeil Metcalf, 51, from Childwall,
OL,12,Fearned #80,000 a year but started
OL,13,Fstealing after maxing out his credit
OL,14,Fcards, racking up a debt of #100,000.
OL,16,FMetcalf worked at St Anthony of Padua
OL,17,FCatholic Primary School and Our Lady's
OL,18,FBishop Eton Catholic Primary School in
OL,19,FMossley Hill, Liverpool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
