OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FHe was previously described as
OL,8,F"precisely the sort one would want in
OL,9,Fleadership in a school", motivating
OL,10,Fstudents and inspiring confidence.
OL,12,FBut he was abusing his trusted
OL,13,Fposition to steal money from the two
OL,14,Fschools after building up a huge debt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
