OL,3,CHeadteacher stole from two schools
OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FThe 51-year-old, of Jubilee Avenue in
OL,8,FChildwall, Liverpool, sent the money
OL,9,Fin the form of cheques to his
OL,10,Funsuspecting stepson, with
OL,11,Finstructions to transfer the money
OL,12,Finto his personal bank account once
OL,13,Fthe cheques had cleared.
OL,15,FHe made six fraudulent payments of
OL,16,F#1,800 each, totalling #10,800, from
OL,17,FSt Anthony of Padua Catholic Primary
OL,18,FSchool between September 2017 and May
OL,19,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
