OL,3,CHeadteacher stole from two schools
OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FHe made three fraudulent payments of
OL,8,F#2,160, #250 and #2,280 from Our
OL,9,FLady's Bishop Eton Catholic Primary
OL,10,FSchool between September 2022 and
OL,11,FSeptember 2023 - adding up to a grand
OL,12,Ftotal of #15,490. He pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Ftwo counts of fraud by abuse of
OL,14,Fposition in Liverpool Crown Court last
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,17,FHis offending was discovered when the
OL,18,Ffinance officer at Our Lady's Bishop
OL,19,FEton noticed an unusual invoice made
OL,20,Fout to a company called "School Fit"
OL,21,Fand "J. Neil".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
