OL,3,CHeadteacher stole from two schools
OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FShe asked Metcalf about the payment,
OL,8,Fand he told her it was for "health and
OL,9,Fsafety".
OL,11,FProsecutor Callum Ross, at court
OL,12,Ftoday, August 19, said: "The officer
OL,13,Frecalled how Neil was the surname of
OL,14,Fthe defendant's stepson, who was
OL,15,Fcalled Joseph. That made her
OL,16,Fsuspicious.
OL,18,F"She then googled School Fit as a
OL,19,Fresult of her concerns and could find
OL,20,Fno information on that company at all.
OL,21,FThe VAT number was also invalid."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
