OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FMr Ross said Metcalf - who earned
OL,8,F#80,000 a year as a headteacher - had
OL,9,Fcommitted "an abuse of a position of
OL,10,Fpower and trust and responsibility".
OL,12,FHe said: "Where St Anthony's is
OL,13,Fconcerned they say the money could
OL,14,Fhave been put to better use. It was
OL,15,Fnot an insignificant amount of money
OL,16,Ffor a school which relies on resources
OL,17,Fto further the children's education.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
