OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FHe said: "At 51 he's mortified he
OL,8,Ffound himself in the dock at a crown
OL,9,Fcourt. He has enjoyed a positive
OL,10,Fcareer dedicated to teaching children
OL,11,Fin Merseyside and supporting them to
OL,12,Fachieve their best.
OL,14,F"Former colleagues regard him as
OL,15,Fprofessional and precisely the sort
OL,16,Fone would want in leadership in a
OL,17,Fschool. Former students say he gave
OL,18,Fthem confidence in their abilities and
OL,19,Fwas motivational and kind."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
