OL,4,Cafter racking up #100,000 credit card
OL,5,Cdebt
OL,7,FSentencing Metcalf to 15 months in
OL,8,Fprison, judge Mark Ainsworth said:
OL,9,F"It's clear that you were an excellent
OL,10,Fteacher and you were an effective
OL,11,Fleader. Plainly as a headteacher you
OL,12,Fhad a particularly high position of
OL,13,Fauthority."
OL,15,FHe added: "I fully accept these
OL,16,Fconvictions will bring an end to your
OL,17,Fprofessional career and while it may
OL,18,Fbe you can serve the community in the
OL,19,Ffuture, it will not be as a teacher,
OL,20,Fand certainly not a headteacher."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
